<chapter xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0">
  <title>Globals</title>
  <section>
    <title>Introduction</title>
    
    <para>
      <indexterm><primary>globals</primary></indexterm>
      Global constants in TDF-OS are very useful for development if you
      know what they are. Here are the global constants grouped by their
      header files, excluding those in <filename
      class="headerfile">MPX_SUPT.H</filename>
    </para>
  </section>
  
